(77,1,"2018-03-11 18:25:43","2018-03-11 18:25:43","We understand that one of the most important criterion to a successful implementation is the ease to which the system can provide the proper visibility to your data.  Often times a report or dashboard is viewed by the highest levels of management.  This data must be presented in a clear and consise format with the ability to \"drill down\" to the underlying data.  A system designed by Design First shows not only the data that is needed to run your business, but also the data that can show how well your system is utilized and accepted.\r\n\r\nSome sample metrics that our clients follow are:\r\n\r\n[list type=\"check\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>For Sales Managers: Pipeline Trends, Closed Sales vs. Quota, and Sales Life-Cycle</li>\r\n 	<li>For Marketing Managers: Campaign ROI, Lead Generation, and Product Pipelines</li>\r\n 	<li>For Service Managers: Open Cases by Service Rep, Client Satisfaction, and Escalated Cases</li>\r\n 	<li>For C-Level Managers: Sales YTD, Quarterly Forecasts, and Adoption Metrics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/list]\r\n\r\nThe key concept is displaying the data to the user (no matter what level within the organization the user resides) in a way that is easy to read, easy to understand, and puts them in the best position to make the right decision.","Future Insights","","inherit","closed","closed","","57-revision-v1","","","2018-03-11 18:25:43","2018-03-11 18:25:43","",57,"http://designfirst.local/57-revision-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
