(79,1,"2018-03-11 18:27:12","2018-03-11 18:27:12","There has been a paradigm shift in the way people communicate.  People are now using social platforms to share information in ways that did not exist ten years ago.\r\n\r\nSalesforce.com\'s social platform, Chatter, has revolutionized corporate communication in the same way.\r\n\r\nChatter can, all under the security of Salesforce.com’s secure platform:\r\n\r\n[list type=\"check\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Reduce email clutter and noise</li>\r\n 	<li>Centralize communication threads</li>\r\n 	<li>Serve as a repository of information</li>\r\n 	<li>Increase the ease of internal collaboration</li>\r\n 	<li>Share knowledge</li>\r\n 	<li>Provide a familiar way for your employees to communicate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/list]\r\n\r\nHere is how Design First clients are using Chatter today.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Project Collaboration</li>\r\n 	<li>Real-time updates on important Opportunities and Accounts</li>\r\n 	<li>Corporate Announcements</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nHow will your company socialize?","Let\'s Get Social","","inherit","closed","closed","","56-revision-v1","","","2018-03-11 18:27:12","2018-03-11 18:27:12","",56,"http://designfirst.local/56-revision-v1/",0,"revision","",0),
